==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Serricorn
<hw>Ser"ri*corn</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of a
numerous tribe of beetles (<fam>Serricornia</fam>). The joints of the
antennae are prominent, thus producing a serrate appearance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Serried</ent>⟦br⟧
